testcase.name: given an event with a source not supported by any child logger when log is called then it should throw LogSourceNotSupportedException
given an event supported by one source when log is called then it should be logged just to the child logger that support the source
given an event supported by multiple source when log is called then it should be logged is all the sources
given a unique identifier for the event when identify is called then it should identify in all the loggers
